
  python3 -m venv venv               
  source venv/bin/activate           


2. Installation



   git clone https://github.com/sourcegraph/lsif-py.git
   cd lsif-py


   pip install -r requirements.txt


   pip install .


3. Running the Indexer


   
   ./lsif-py lsif_indexer <path-to-your-workspace>
   
   
   
   ./lsif-py -v lsif_indexer <workspace>
  
   
   ./lsif-py lsif_indexer -o myindex.lsif <workspace>
 

